{"tid":577622,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"阿記主場鬥曼城  入座率只得5成","createTime":"2018-03-02T02:09:11.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-02T03:05:34.000Z","uid":58022,"like":15,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"6fa9c52b23056807cf9a728a6bebeb16ffe4194a","tid":577622,"uid":58022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T02:09:11.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=tzihyB9kHcV2KeLkcst4sozZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=ee20f247\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】阿仙奴周四聯賽主場再吞曼城3蛋，球迷爆料稱曼城球迷高歌：世界上只有一個雲加。<br />\n<br />\n阿仙奴繼上場英聯盃決賽後，周四聯賽在主場再輸0:3，短短4日吞掉曼城6隻蛋，球迷怎能不氣憤？其實主隊球迷已有心理準備，周四主場竟然出現近一半空凳，認真「無眼屎乾净盲」。入場球迷賽後還在社交網站爆料，稱有曼城球迷高歌：世上只有一個雲加，令主場球迷情何以堪？<br />\n<br />\n「The Wenger Out」在Twitter寫道：「他們還唱：雲加，留下吧！這對阿仙奴意味甚麼？高安基！有膽！今晚就炒掉雲加吧！事情繼續下去，不會有任何改善的！」「Jew on the Right」則寫道：「地球上沒有人比雲加更值得炒！我的身份是曼城球迷。」另有球迷嘲諷射失12碼的奧巴美揚：「歡迎加盟阿仙奴！」意指這樣的表現才符合阿仙奴風格。<br />\n<br />\n對高安基等高層而言，球迷的抗議沒有用，但如果場場主場都得40000多人入場，卻是很有力的表態。當迎戰榜首曼城球迷也不願入場，阿仙奴已經響起警號，高層應該聽得見。<br />\n<br />\n圖片來源 : &copy;AFP<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/02/100738_05447d13766c2d838d31906150d9da2c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F02%2F100738_05447d13766c2d838d31906150d9da2c.png&h=76a1403a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n阿妓主場變鏝主場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n全世界一齊迫害爺爺  <br />\n無人性<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n爺爺幫你地不敗奪冠無人記得了"},{"pid":"4d39699c4d260f301adaa9f27045b55e5949ee6e","tid":577622,"uid":157193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T02:10:21.000Z","msg":"慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8293a865ff622d8b19af9b2198ad248759ceae9e","tid":577622,"uid":799,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T02:11:09.000Z","msg":"死老野 自己走啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4001c97dcd6307589001b0923142d4b8158132f8","tid":577622,"uid":555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T02:12:03.000Z","msg":"大風大雪點出去睇呀"},{"pid":"b9f7b9e09ab3b184681d7cbfe269be913cb4f506","tid":577622,"uid":58552,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T02:12:46.000Z","msg":"10-2輸 拜仁都係咁啦 慣哂啦"},{"pid":"8a7d31253f6f1eeb600cb5f35c114bdeb3df211e","tid":577622,"uid":53736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T02:13:50.000Z","msg":"無雲加呢隊垃圾仲撚難攪<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a780c2650dae93e95c180865f07ef8d9c6d3f9a7","tid":577622,"uid":157193,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"b9f7b9e09ab3b184681d7cbfe269be913cb4f506","tid":577622,"uid":58552,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T02:12:46.000Z","msg":"10-2輸 拜仁都係咁啦 慣哂啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T02:14:11.000Z","msg":"起碼有兩粒入<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e2517485f26def9dd783d86a3ef627e69d55d7e","tid":577622,"uid":4180,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T02:14:34.000Z","msg":"唔係雲加你班友有球場坐?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1dfa32dbd4152e3dbf8b0054e409a88f313b40c8","tid":577622,"uid":58022,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4e2517485f26def9dd783d86a3ef627e69d55d7e","tid":577622,"uid":4180,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T02:14:34.000Z","msg":"唔係雲加你班友有球場坐?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry